---
title: Salmon with Dilly Crème Fraîche & Asparagus Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Pan-seared salmon already feels luxe. Add a crème fraîche sauce speckled with herbaceous chopped dill, and you’ll elevate your dinner to restaurant-quality—all in under 20 minutes. Serve alongside fluffy couscous and snappy sautéed asparagus for fanciness in a flash.
